      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"8. ROMA KEEPING finds it hard to win but has a consistent overall record, having placed eight of 14 career runs. Has finished in the money at the last three runs. Goes very well here finding the frame in each of three starts. Deserves a win and gets her chance. 6. HOOKED ON DOLLY ran good time (36.51) when second last start over 620m at Casino, the second placing in a row. Well placed here and should do much better. 3. SCARBOROUGH PEST settled midfield in the run and boxed on to finish there when 4th (34.90) at this track. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from three starts. Has ability and can measure up. 4. WATCH MY SIX is one of the chances after collecting a minor prize last time.\",\"runners\":[8,6,3,4],\"exclusive\":false}",
